{
  "stem": "21310.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew I couldn't drink.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I made a deal with the woman who had the concession that whenever I came with somebody she should pour or give me water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they drink vodka in a glass, just straight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- so she was very happy, and she would serve the-- the water to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would drink, and I got the reputation that I really can hold my whiskey.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgot that it was water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I came to this country, vodka was just becoming popular.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went to a party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somebody asked me what-- you know, the host was so pleased.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had vodka and whatnot, what will I have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, vodka.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, how do you want it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, what do you mean how I want it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Straight.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I still had this idea that I really can hold my-- my liquor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he gave me a little vodka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You even fooled yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I drank it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and boy, did I get drunk on [LAUGHS] that one shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the big joke was, you know, oh, Edith's the one who can hold her liquor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But it's funny how you forget certain things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One time there was a train coming from Warsaw with Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it stopped at the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were looking out these tiny windows with the wires in front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, some of them had tin cups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were begging for waters-- and for water-- and I was scared silly that they would recognize me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And yet, I wanted to know who was on-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they organized, like two other women, that help me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the train stopped maybe for half an hour or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was a pump.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
